    { heading: 'How Our AI Advantage Prevents Data Loss', text: 'The detailed AI section. Explain the specific automation workflows for backup verification, anomaly detection (potential ransomware), and automated recovery sequencing.' },
    { heading: 'One Solution for Your Entire Tech Stack', text: 'Address the scope. Detail the types of data and systems covered: servers (virtual & physical), Microsoft 365, Google Workspace, databases, and critical applications.' },
    { heading: 'The AI Advantage', text: 'Our AI Advantage for Backup & Recovery is not a buzzword; it\'s a system of automated workflows that ensures your data is always safe and recoverable. Our platform continuously runs Automated Backup Verification, where an AI agent mounts every backup in an isolated sandbox and checks for file system integrity, ensuring it\'s not corrupted. Simultaneously, our Predictive Anomaly Detection engine analyzes file change rates; if it detects a sudden spike in encrypted files, it flags a potential ran...' },
    { heading: 'Proven Results', stats: [{ value: '<15-minute', label: 'Recovery Time Objective (RTO) guaranteed,' }, { value: '99.99%', label: 'backup success rate, verified by AI,' }, { value: '15-Minute', label: 'Recovery Guarantee' }] }
